```class Solution {
    public int reachNumber(int target) {
        target = Math.abs(target);
        int sum = 0, steps = 0;
        while (sum < target) {
            steps++;
            sum += steps;
        }
        if ((sum - target) % 2 == 1) {
            steps++;
        }
        return steps;
    }
}```
